%% Status: NEEDS HUMAN REVIEW
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> COLD_START

    state "COLD_START" as COLD_START
    state "RESTORING_SESSION" as RESTORING_SESSION
    state "UNAUTHENTICATED" as UNAUTHENTICATED
    state "AUTHENTICATING" as AUTHENTICATING
    state "HYDRATING" as HYDRATING
    state "ACTIVE" as ACTIVE
    state "BACKGROUNDED" as BACKGROUNDED
    state "RECAP_CHECK" as RECAP_CHECK
    state "SHOWING_RECAP" as SHOWING_RECAP
    state "ERROR" as ERROR

    note right of COLD_START
        App launched, no state.
    end note

    note right of RESTORING_SESSION
        Check Supabase for existing
        auth session.
    end note

    note right of UNAUTHENTICATED
        No valid session.
        Show LoginScreen.
    end note

    note right of HYDRATING
        Session valid.
        Fetching items + species data
        from Supabase.
    end note

    note right of ACTIVE
        App ready, user interacting.
    end note

    note right of BACKGROUNDED
        App in background (mobile)
        or tab hidden (web).
    end note

    note right of RECAP_CHECK
        On foreground, check if 6h+
        since last recap.
    end note

    note right of SHOWING_RECAP
        Recap card stack displayed.
    end note

    COLD_START --> RESTORING_SESSION : app init

    RESTORING_SESSION --> HYDRATING : session found & valid
    RESTORING_SESSION --> UNAUTHENTICATED : no session / expired
    RESTORING_SESSION --> ERROR : auth check failed

    UNAUTHENTICATED --> AUTHENTICATING : user taps sign‑in

    AUTHENTICATING --> HYDRATING : auth success
    AUTHENTICATING --> UNAUTHENTICATED : auth cancelled
    AUTHENTICATING --> ERROR : auth error

    HYDRATING --> ACTIVE : data loaded
    HYDRATING --> ERROR : data fetch failed

    ACTIVE --> BACKGROUNDED : app backgrounded / tab hidden
    ACTIVE --> UNAUTHENTICATED : sign out

    BACKGROUNDED --> RECAP_CHECK : app foregrounded

    RECAP_CHECK --> SHOWING_RECAP : 6h+ since last recap
    RECAP_CHECK --> ACTIVE : less than 6h, skip recap

    SHOWING_RECAP --> ACTIVE : recap dismissed

    ERROR --> RESTORING_SESSION : retry
    ERROR --> UNAUTHENTICATED : back to login
